				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-686053#post-2177596</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-686053/scp-1363#post-2177596</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2014 02:25:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Agent MacLeod</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1922529</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This. Is. How. You. Skipify. History. This. Is. How. You. Skipify. Real. People. Not by making Hitler a Gatling Gun toting cyborg, not by making Joan of Ark the victim of a sadistic Lovecraftian entity, not by making Julius Cesar a reptilian alien, not by making Shi Huangdi a reality bender. You take the people who played God, and you make it clear that God played back.</p> <p>Take notes, ladies, gentlemen, and other respectable entities. This is art.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
