					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&#8230; I has a suspicion.</p> <p>*Checks up Demon Core on Wikipedia*</p> <p>HAH! I was right.</p> <p>It makes me wonder if there was something itself about that core that caused these two to.. well, become something else after their death, rather than all the other folks that have died in nuclear accidents.</p> <p>It's also interesting that the stages of the virus *exactly mimic* the symptoms of radiation poisoning. I would think the Foundation would have noted that.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
